state.modify { state -> Event? in
					switch event {
					case let .value(value):
						switch state {
						case .throttled:
							state = .throttled(value)
							return nil
						case .resumed:
							return event
						case .terminated:
							return nil
						}

					case .completed, .interrupted, .failed:
						state = .terminated
						return event
					}
				}
